<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="46" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,565,2031]" pageId="1" pageNumber="46">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,327,645,671]" pageId="1" pageNumber="46">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Integument striated; coxal surface reticulated; P- 
<number box="[941,954,645,671]" pageId="1" pageNumber="46" value="3.0">3</number>
longer than the P- 
<number box="[1195,1210,645,671]" pageId="1" pageNumber="46" value="4.0">4</number>
